were too tight one officer said next time ill put them on so 
tight theyll make you cry 
the allegations of rough treatment resulted in three days of 
protests by minority students and a promise by asu administrators 
to take steps to reduce racism on campus 
small said the fbi investigation could take several months to 
complete 
