ten years after the may 3 1979 election that 
brought margaret thatcher to power most britons want her to step 
down soon and think her rightwing revolution has gone too far 
according to new polls 
but while britons questioned ahead of wednesdays anniversary 
say they dont like her the likelihood is they will go on voting 
