characters same plots not funny not fresh somebody sent me this 
script called tapeheads and we saw the name and said lets do 
it 
it sounded really sick he said it was a black comedy on 
the music business and i got to finally play a guy who wasnt a 
good guy who would sell out his mother for the right price 
