about 4500 active employees and has entered chapter 11 bankruptcy 
reorganization and protection from creditors 
parent texas air corp plans to rebuild eastern as a smaller 
airline without the unions but the unions are optimistic that new 
ownership for the entire airline still can be found even though 
eastern insists that none of the offers it has received are viable 
