polaroid corp took great pains to avoid 
competition with wellestablished eastman kodak co the polaroid 
chairman testified today as a court tried to determine how much 
kodak should pay for infringing on its rivals instantphotography 
technology 
chairman william j mccune jr the opening witness of the 
